calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund private company information  bloomberg july    am et capital markets company overview of calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund snapshot people company overview calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund is an open ended equity indexed mutual fund launched and managed by calvert research and management it invests in the public equity markets of the united states the fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors it primarily invests in stocks of socially conscious largecap companies the fund seeks to replicate the performance of the calvert us large cap core responsible index by investing in stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index it does not invest in stocks of companies that demonstrate poor environmental performance or compliance records  calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund is an open ended equity indexed mutual fund launched and managed by calvert research and management it invests in the public equity markets of the united states the fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors it primarily invests in stocks of socially conscious largecap companies the fund seeks to replicate the performance of the calvert us large cap core responsible index by investing in stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index it does not invest in stocks of companies that demonstrate poor environmental performance or compliance records contribute significantly to local or global environmental problems or include risks related to the operation of nuclear power facilities are the subject of serious laborrelated actions or penalties by regulatory agencies exhibit a pattern and practice of human rights violations demonstrate poor corporate governance manufacture tobacco products and firearms andor ammunition have significant and direct involvement in the manufacture of alcoholic beverages or gambling operations abuse animals cause unnecessary suffering and death of animals and develop geneticallymodified organisms for environmental release without countervailing social benefits the fund was formerly known as calvert social index series inc  calvert social index fund calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund was formed on june   and is domiciled in the united states detailed description  montgomery avebethesda md united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwcalvertcomstrategiesstrategiesbyproductmutualfundscalvertuslargecapcoreresponsbile key executives for calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund mr donald wayne silby esq chairman and president age  mr robert j kay head of investor relations mr michael v yuhas controller age  mr andrew kurt niebler esq vice president and deputy general counsel age  ms jane bardeen maxwell esq executive officer age  compensation as of fiscal year  calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund key developments calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund specialextraordinary shareholders meeting feb   jan   calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund specialextraordinary shareholders meeting feb   at  us eastern standard time location  montgomery avenue suite n bethesda maryland united states calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund specialextraordinary shareholders meeting dec   nov   calvert responsible index series inc  calvert us large cap core responsible index fund specialextraordinary shareholders meeting dec   at  us eastern standard time location  montgomery avenue suite n bethesda md  united states agenda to consider the election of 